      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 395&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>red&nbsp;onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) the <strong>ginger&nbsp;</strong>and finely chop (or grate)</p>",
